description: Jetpak Top Holding AB engages in the provision of time critical express deliveries. The company is headquartered in Solna, Stockholm and currently employs 214 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2018-12-05. The firm provides time-critical express deliveries in the Nordic region, as well as several other European countries. The company specializes in flight-based, door-to-door, long-distance deliveries aimed primarily at the business to business (B2B) sector. The firm's uses its information technology (IT) platform JENA to find the optimal transport route, combining air and road transport. The firm operates through two segments: Express Ad-hoc and Express Systemized. Express Ad-hoc segment comprises ad-hoc orders for flexible and time-critical courier services. Express Systemized segment comprises systematic orders for parcel shipments. The firm's point-to-point network covers more than 150 locations.
name: Jetpak Top Holding AB (publ)
